  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/1c98fcf63cb0d68b440c49ec570bc2c3.avif?t=1707744416\" width=533 height=78 /></span><br>Dive headfirst into this 3D action/racing game, run at full speed, jump to avoid dangers and hit the finish line! More than thirty different levels await you, with missions and medals to earn at each level. You won't be short of challenges!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/9b3363027aee936c82cb69d42eaf4297.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/9b3363027aee936c82cb69d42eaf4297.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help Voulpy in his adventure! </strong></h2>His little brother has been kidnapped and it's up to you to travel through various worlds to find him! Beaches, jungles, snowy mountains, flaming dungeons, but be careful not to end up as crab bait...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/d6692e15870e605aff8c1bc5ccdc60dd.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/d6692e15870e605aff8c1bc5ccdc60dd.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the coolest kraken on the islands!</strong></h2>The game has a multitude of costumes to unlock, pirate or unicorn - it's up to you to choose.<br>So if you love octopuses, the beach, and adventure, set out on an adventure in Kraken Odyssey!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/3d3f449fab0587ae5ab8d92feaa460c2.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/3d3f449fab0587ae5ab8d92feaa460c2.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/73c310eb9c727f0cfc4761b49dabb095.avif?t=1707744416\" width=515 height=245 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/1c98fcf63cb0d68b440c49ec570bc2c3.avif?t=1707744416\" width=533 height=78 /></span><br>Dive headfirst into this 3D action/racing game, run at full speed, jump to avoid dangers and hit the finish line! More than thirty different levels await you, with missions and medals to earn at each level. You won't be short of challenges!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/9b3363027aee936c82cb69d42eaf4297.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/9b3363027aee936c82cb69d42eaf4297.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help Voulpy in his adventure! </strong></h2>His little brother has been kidnapped and it's up to you to travel through various worlds to find him! Beaches, jungles, snowy mountains, flaming dungeons, but be careful not to end up as crab bait...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/d6692e15870e605aff8c1bc5ccdc60dd.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/d6692e15870e605aff8c1bc5ccdc60dd.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the coolest kraken on the islands!</strong></h2>The game has a multitude of costumes to unlock, pirate or unicorn - it's up to you to choose.<br>So if you love octopuses, the beach, and adventure, set out on an adventure in Kraken Odyssey!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/3d3f449fab0587ae5ab8d92feaa460c2.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/3d3f449fab0587ae5ab8d92feaa460c2.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/73c310eb9c727f0cfc4761b49dabb095.avif?t=1707744416\" width=515 height=245 /></span>",
